      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that's ready for its next journey? This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a reliable performer that will get you where you need to go with confidence. It's a great value for anyone seeking a solid, functional ride!",
